[size=5]Data Files[/size][list]
[*]The shipping data is saved as a CSV in the SproutSight Mod directory. It follows the filename pattern [code]<FarmerName>_<UniqueSaveId>.csv[/code]
[*]The wallet and cash flow data is saved as a CSV in the SproutSight Mod directory. It follows the filename pattern [code]<FarmerName>_<UniqueSaveId>_gold.csv[/code]
